                    .headline
                        span.h3 What is STC - Database B3-549
                    p
                        | Star Trek Corpora (or STC) is a project that started out of the desire to get information about my
                        | favorite tv serie : Star Trek.
                        | At first I wanted to have access to Voyager (VOY) dialogs to analyse them and come up with some sort of
                        | primitive natural language generator,
                        | then I searched online for Star Trek API but I could not find such a thing, I found Pok√©API and SWAPI
                        | (Star Wars API) and got inspired. What if I could assemble enough data
                        | to provide some model with rudimentary natural language (dialog act, really) generation capabilities ?
                    p
                        | So I started gathering data....
                    p
                        | and gathered more than I expected to have, at first it was all about Voyager, but then as I watched Next
                        | Generation I started to be interested in a broader spectrum for this project...I started gathering all
                        | things star trek and then, I finally have some decent amount of data available for you to play with!
                    br
                    p
                        | I have not yet completed the natural language generator, as it is a very complex endeavour, but I have
                        | assembled a lot of data for anyone interested to play with it.
                        | I will try to keep updating the data as time passes, but I want to give the NLG (natural language
                        | generator) a maximum of time and effort.
                    p
                        | The Star Trek Corpora API is not an exhaustive Star Trek API, as there are a lot of data missing, but
                        | there is enough to match the dialogs context, which is what this project is all about.
                    p
                        | Star Trek Corpora API (STCAPI) is a REST API and is not yet MS Guidelines compliant, as this is an ALPHA.
                        | See the documentation to get started.

